lead_paragraph: Yasmani Grandal, who hadn't hit a home run on the road this season, was just trying to get on base after working a 3-0 count with two outs in the fourth inning.

headline.print_headline: Dodgers Belt 3 Home Runs in 8-1 Rout of Brewers
